verses.text:
Wherefore remember, that ye \add being\add* in time past Gentiles
in the flesh, who are called Uncircumcision by that which is called
the Circumcision in the flesh made by hands;

Having abolished in his flesh the enmity, \add even\add* the
law of commandments \add contained\add* in ordinances; for to make
in himself of twain one new man, \add so\add* making peace;

Which in other ages was not made known unto the sons of men,
as it is now revealed unto his holy apostles and prophets by the
Spirit;

Unto me, who am less than the least of all saints, is this
grace given, that I should preach among the Gentiles the unsearchable
riches of Christ;

Servants, be obedient to them that are \add your\add* masters
according to the flesh, with fear and trembling, in singleness of
your heart, as unto Christ;

Praying always with all prayer and supplication in the Spirit,
and watching thereunto with all perseverance and supplication for
all saints;
